summary: Changes the sunsprite for ENB v0.119 into a more realistic version.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mini-mod, nothing special, but I like it. 
It changes the sunsprite for ENB v0.119 into a more realistic version.

Install the original ENB by Boris Vorontsov, backup the old enbsunsprite.tga file in your skyrim folder (not data!) and overwrite with my enbsunsprite.tga 

Link to ENB: http://www.enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.htm

Endorse if you like and credit me if you use it somewhere else.

Cheers
author: Pfaffendrill
